---
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About - Your Business</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white text-gray-900" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">

    <header class="py-10">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col items-center gap-8">
        <a href="/" class="text-3xl tracking-widest uppercase" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Your Business</a>
        <nav class="flex gap-10 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-700">
          <a href="/" class="hover:text-black">Home</a>
          <a href="/about" class="hover:text-black">About</a>
          <a href="/services" class="hover:text-black">Services</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-black">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-28">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 mb-4 text-center">Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl mb-10 text-center leading-tight" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
        About Us
      </h1>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-700 font-light leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          We believe every business deserves a strong online presence—without paying premium agency prices.
        </p>
        <p>
          We specialize in building clean, modern websites and practical marketing systems designed for small businesses, startups, and founders who want results without complexity. Our focus is simple: create websites that look professional, load fast, and actually convert visitors into customers.
        </p>
        <p>
          Unlike traditional agencies, we keep things lean. No bloated fees, no unnecessary add-ons—just what your business needs to grow. From website design to basic marketing automation, we help you get online quickly and start generating real traction.

Whether you're just starting out or upgrading your current site, we make the process straightforward, affordable, and effective.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="border-t border-gray-200 py-12">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-2xl tracking-widest uppercase mb-6" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Your Business</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 tracking-wide">&copy; 2026 Tashi's Design. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>